=== TEST 1: the "substitution" command with default types
--- main_config
    load_module /etc/nginx/modules/ngx_http_subs_filter_module.so;
--- config
    location / {
        subs_filter 'tom' 'yaoweibin' ir;
        root html;
    }
--- user_files
>>> a.html
tom and jerry
--- request
    GET /a.html
--- response_body_unlike: ^(.*)tom(.*)$

